Doctors' attire has known to impact patients' trust and confidence for better clinical practice.

 However, few survey research regarding this topic has been conducted in traditional asian medicine field.

 The aim of our study is to determine whether traditional medicine doctor's attire impacts on patients' confidence and trust.

